## Part 0: Testing Philosophy (1 hour)

### 0.1 What to Test

**Test these:**
- Business logic (the "why" decisions)
- Data validation
- Error handling
- Edge cases

**Don't test:**
- Standard library functions (go/database/sql works fine)
- External services (use mocks)
- Simple getters/setters
- Code with no logic

### 0.2 Test Pyramid

```
        UI Tests (few)
           /\
          /  \
         /    \
        /      \
       /        \
      / Service  \     (integration tests)
     /   Tests    \
    /              \
   /________________\
  /                  \
 /  Unit Tests        \  (many - fast - run often)
/____________________ \
```

